{"tid":404377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[何君堯：殺豬殺狗不是一回事] 殺狗被判入獄案例","createTime":"2017-09-18T05:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T01:26:36.000Z","uid":136994,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfc05e7f6f8fc88f103ef2f9ba4b336477351d10","tid":404377,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:09:30.000Z","msg":"身為律師嘅何君堯竟然話「殺豬殺狗不是一回事」呀嘛<br />\n咁一於就回顧吓殺狗被判入冊通櫃嘅案例啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. <br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-188627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.am730.com.hk%2Farticle-188627&d=r%2F0d4hx8Jr8mhOBff1Uf6cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=96ae91c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://archive.am730.com.hk/article-188627</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">64歲的前市政總署職員曾海棠，於去年9月，在元朗大樹下西路南坑排附近，放置沾有殺蟲藥的有毒雞肉，一隻流浪狗進食後被毒死</span>，曾海棠被捕後聲稱妻子晨運時遇流浪狗受驚，故毒殺流浪狗報仇。曾海棠早前承認一項殘酷對待動物罪名，<span style=\"color: red;\">屯門裁判法院昨判其監禁2個月</span>。署任主任裁判官李唯治批評被告非常冷血、殘忍和自私，認為在文明社會，所有動動物都應有生存以及與其他生物共存的權利，不容許執行私刑。<br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170807/57052137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170807%2F57052137&d=r%2F0d4hx8Jr8mhOBff1Uf6cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=18e197e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170807%2F57052137&h=196544c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170807/57052137</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">地盤工人留宿戒毒所時聲稱遭院內唐狗咬傷，遂聯同另一院友對唐狗拳打腳踢，地盤工用繩綁著唐狗的頸，把唐狗拋落斜坡及用水喉掃射。狗屍兩日後被發現，屍體嚴重腐爛至無法剖驗</span>，工人早前承認虐畜罪，今年5月被判監3個月。律政司認為判刑過輕申請覆核判刑，裁判官今批准申請，原定明天出獄的被告被加刑1個月。<br />\n<br />\n控方指本案涉及違反誠信，狗隻失去知覺後被告馮志凱（26歲）沒尋求協助，故要求將量刑起點調升至8至14個月。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官考慮控方案例及早前陳詞後，認同量刑起點有上調空間，將原定4個月的起點增至6個月，開審前認罪減刑四分之一，判監4個月2星期，但考慮被告等候覆核聆訊期間的壓力，及在即將放監才被加刑，故額外減刑2周，<span style=\"color: red;\">總判刑4個月</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，被告曾一度棄保潛逃，之後自首認罪。裁判官今指他是在正式被檢控、定下聆訊日子後缺席，他自首不應成為扣減刑期因素，否則變相鼓勵面對審訊的被告人缺席聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n3. <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20130214/51264284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20130214%2F51264284&d=r%2F0d4hx8Jr8mhOBff1Uf6cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=3430cdb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20130214%2F51264284&h=00e115e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20130214/51264284</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">31歲的電腦技術員莫仲霆，家中餵養兩隻貓的電腦技術員，聲稱不堪遭附近村屋的唐狗吠叫滋擾，去年9月竟然向陳氏養的唐狗淋潑天拿水，繼而點火燒狗，令小狗最後因重傷遭人道毀滅。</span>莫早前承認一項殘酷對待動物罪，<span style=\"color: red;\">今在屯門裁判法院被判入獄八個月</span>。<br />\n<br />\n莫的居所和狗隻身處的地方相距140米，被告又住在15樓，法官認為被告指感到受騷擾只是主觀感覺，未必來自同一隻狗，形容被告行為殘忍、滅絕人性，而且非一時衝動。鑑於加上近期較多虐待動物的個案，必須判處具阻嚇性刑罰，遂判監禁八個月。<br />\n<br />\n4. <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20061223/6649031\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20061223%2F6649031&d=r%2F0d4hx8Jr8mhOBff1Uf6cP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=93b46b5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20061223%2F6649031&h=acff5a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20061223/6649031</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">四名中年漢欲進補，竟將兩頭飼養狗隻宰殺烹煮</span>，四人早前承認屠宰狗隻作食物罪名，案件昨在屯門裁判法院宣判，律師求情指，過往並沒有判監案例，本案沒有虐畜成份，純屬飲食文化問題，盼法庭輕判。主任裁判官郭偉健則表示，狗為人類忠心朋友，法庭要帶出現今社會不容狗的訊息，必須監禁，但考慮這是立法半世紀以來首宗同類判監案件，<span style=\"color: red;\">酌減四被告的刑期為各入獄30天。</span>"},{"pid":"f7838fd1f0917aa6ccaca3babdfca74e502d29df","tid":404377,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca453ef2e30020c4a0e8373d0b282bda980f937","tid":404377,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:38:41.000Z","msg":"點解個垃圾做到律師"},{"pid":"10031245c5735e487101f23c1de6217717cbbf3e","tid":404377,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43c1c9d87c36e6509f566abe7cf101ee4ba14f4","tid":404377,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec670868e4d9c37aa1062030e536570b4015512","tid":404377,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/0/05/ZEKF1lm.gif/revision/latest?cb=20130614182427\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F0%2F05%2FZEKF1lm.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130614182427&h=1f13efd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90798827f9f60da4146dff1a422b12340221e82e","tid":404377,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f38c9355e6e65c811485e1a19dd1282e2db32e","tid":404377,"uid":136994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:08:50.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n做律師唔係要識好多案例咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n殺豬殺狗點撚可能唔係一回事<br />\n何君妖真係影撚衰晒法律專業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebb943c5261b7d7b232b902e7a27bf7dcc8e960","tid":404377,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T09:45:12.000Z","msg":"有冇動物權益人士一齊譴責何君妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5089ee999a1f0c852f56ead812bb7a8be9e028","tid":404377,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e581f746caad5497fadd761e57b31262303381b8","tid":404377,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇動物權益人士一齊譴責何君妖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e849e63a2e0fc00f1c3be790668d28cdb8f0c1f4","tid":404377,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"殺狗就一定犯法，但殺豬都要持牌屠場喎"},{"pid":"dc3ccec281fbcc1d76738b74367299fb898426e5","tid":404377,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T12:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6508d83af91522c1a0d56007f2248a9f81e48418","tid":404377,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T01:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}